longBusinessSummary: Spectrum Electrical Industries Limited designs, manufactures, and sells electrical, automobile, and irrigation components in India. The company offers distribution boards, enclosures, metal junction boxes, AC boxes, modular electric board panels, mini MCB bases and covers, tools, moulds and dies, electric bulb holders, auto and irrigation equipment, lamp angle holders, EV chargers, and other electrical components. It also offers surface coating, metallic stamping, plastics molding, and end to end solutions. The company was incorporated in 2008 and is based in Mumbai, India.
